      h2.Evidence-Synthesis Evidence Synthesis Academy

  .grid-x.align-center
    .cell.small-6.The-Evidence-Synthesis
      p The Evidence Synthesis Academy is a set of free, online, open-access courses on evidence
        synthesis that are designed to be accessible by broad audiences. The courses have been
        developed by a group of evidence synthesis, health communication, and online training
        professionals at the Brown University Center for Evidence Synthesis in Health.
      p To access the Evidence Synthesis Academy, please visit:
        <a href='https://evsynthacademy.com' target='_blank' data-confirm="#{ @exit_disclaimer }">
        https://evsynthacademy.com <span class='i fas fa-external-link-alt fa-sm'></span></a>.

