  .grid-x.align-center
    .cell.small-6.PROSPERO-is-an-international
      p Cochrane (also known as the Cochrane Collaboration) is an international network of volunteers who conduct
        systematic reviews and meta-analyses. Also available through Cochrane are various resources related to
        the various steps of conducting evidence syntheses.
